Type: Package
Package: LLMRcontent
Title: LLM-Assisted Content Analysis for the Social Sciences
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ali", "Sanaei", , "sanaei@uchicago.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Content analysis in which large language model labels are treated
    as measurements, built on 'LLMR': labels are validated against held-out
    human labels, and the remaining error is carried into corrected estimates.
    Audits state how sensitive a coded conclusion is to the coding choices, and
    sealed archives let a reviewer rerun the analysis.
